PrecisEnactment of the PROVINCIAL EMERGENCIES FINANCIAL ASSISTANCE ORDER NO. 38 - which (a) DECLARES the severe flooding in ALBERTA in the summer of 1999 to be of concern to the federal government, and (b) AUTHORIZES the provision of financial assistance in respect thereof.
